axiom cA_pos : 0 <= cA.`cchoose /\ 0 <= cA.`ochoose /\ 0 <= cA.`cguess /\ 0 <= cA.`oguess /\ 0 < cA.`ochoose + cA.`oguess.

op qH = cA.`ochoose + cA.`oguess.
